OL,3,CHousehold water bills set to rise by
OL,4,C#19 a year
OL,6,FITV News Business and Economics Editor
OL,7,FJoel Hills explains what we may get in
OL,8,Freturn for higher water bills
OL,10,FWater bills in England and Wales are
OL,11,Fset to rise by #19 a year on average
OL,12,Fover the next five years.
OL,14,FEquating to a #94 price hike over that
OL,15,Fperiod, it is a third less than the
OL,16,Fincrease called for by water
OL,17,Fproviders, according to draft
OL,18,Fproposals from Ofwat.
