OL,6,FEstimates suggest that around two
OL,7,Fmillion households can't afford their
OL,8,Fcurrent water bills, making the hike
OL,9,Feven less welcomed.
OL,11,FWater firms had initially proposed
OL,12,Fincreases averaging #144 over five
OL,13,Fyears.
