OL,3,CHousehold water bills set to rise by
OL,4,C#19 a year
OL,6,FUnder the plans, Southern Water
OL,7,Fcustomers will face a #183 increase
OL,8,Fover five years, while Dwr Cymru
OL,9,Fcustomers' bills will go up by #137
OL,10,Fand Yorkshire Water customers will pay
OL,11,F#107 more.
OL,13,FAt the other end of the scale,
OL,14,FAffinity customers will see just an
OL,15,F#11 rise, while SES customers' bills
OL,16,Fwill fall by #34 on the previous five
OL,17,Fyears.
