OL,6,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,7,Fsaid: "Customers want to see radical
OL,8,Fchange in the way water companies care
OL,9,Ffor the environment
OL,11,F"Let me be very clear to water
OL,12,Fcompanies ` we will be closely
OL,13,Fscrutinising the delivery of their
OL,14,Fplans and will hold them to account to
OL,15,Fdeliver real improvements to the
OL,16,Fenvironment and for customers and on
OL,17,Ftheir investment programmes."
