OL,3,CHousehold water bills set to rise by
OL,4,C#19 a year
OL,6,FThe proposals are part of the 2024
OL,7,FPrice Review (PR24) and cover the
OL,8,Fperiod from 1 April 2025 to 31 March
OL,9,F2030, ahead of a final decision at the
OL,10,Fend of the year.
OL,12,FOfwat said the average 21% bill
OL,13,Fincrease, around #19 per year, follows
OL,14,Ffirms' proposals to increase their
OL,15,Ftotal spending by #29 billion, split
OL,16,Fbetween a #5 billion increase in the
OL,17,Fcore costs for running their business
OL,18,Fand a #24 billion rise in spending to
OL,19,Fmeet requirements set by governments
OL,20,Fand for other environmental
OL,21,Fimprovements.
