OL,6,FOfwat said its scrutiny of companies'
OL,7,Fcost proposals, to ensure they deliver
OL,8,Fefficiently, had led to a #16 billion
OL,9,Freduction.
OL,11,FHowever the proposed bill increases
OL,12,Fcome amid public fury around firms'
OL,13,Frampant polluting of waterways with
OL,14,Fsewage spills as they continue to hand
OL,15,Fdividends to shareholders, and bonuses
OL,16,Fto executives ` something which Labour
OL,17,Fhas pledged to clamp down on.
OL,19,FSewage spills into England's rivers
OL,20,Fand seas more than doubled in 2023.
